DOC.brief_summary: This study will evaluate the inter-rater and intra-rater reliability of the Facial Wrinkle Scale with Asian Photonumeric Guide (FWS-A) in Japanese subjects.
DOC.brief_title: Reliability of the Facial Wrinkle Scale in Japanese Subjects
DOC.criteria: Ability to assess facial lines in a mirror Removal of facial jewelry and makeup for study visit Infection or skin disorder affecting the face Planned use of botulinum toxin of any serotype between Screening and Day 1 Planned facial cosmetic procedure between Screening and Day 1 Planned excessive/prolonged sun exposure between Screening and Day 1
